---
// About page
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Paper Trails</title>
    
    <!-- Prevent theme flashing - runs immediately -->
    <style>
        /* Prevent FOUC (Flash of Unstyled Content) */
        html:not([data-theme]) body { visibility: hidden; }
    </style>
    <script>
        (function() {
            try {
                const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme');
                const prefersDark = window.matchMedia && window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches;
                const theme = savedTheme || (prefersDark ? 'dark' : 'light');
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', theme);
            } catch (e) {
                // Fallback to light theme if there's any error
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'light');
            }
            // Make body visible after theme is set
            document.body && (document.body.style.visibility = 'visible');
        })();
    </script>
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --bg-primary: white;
            --bg-secondary: #fefaf8;
            --bg-tertiary: #f8f9fa;
            --text-primary: #333;
            --text-secondary: #666;
            --text-tertiary: #999;
            --border-primary: #f0f0f0;
            --border-secondary: #f5f0eb;
            --accent: #f97316;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] {
            --bg-primary: #111111;
            --bg-secondary: #1a1a1a;
            --bg-tertiary: #242424;
            --text-primary: #f5f5f5;
            --text-secondary: #d1d1d1;
            --text-tertiary: #a0a0a0;
            --border-primary: #333333;
            --border-secondary: #2a2a2a;
            --accent: #f97316;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .header-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 40px;
            height: 80px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .logo::before {
            content: "PT";
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #f97316;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: white;
        }

        .header-nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Page header */
        .page-header {
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-secondary);
        }

        .page-header-content {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .page-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 60px 40px 80px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin: 40px 0 20px;
        }

        .content h2:first-of-type {
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .content ul {
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding-left: 24px;
        }

        .content li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .content a {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .content a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        .highlight-box p {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header-content {
                padding: 0 24px;
                height: 70px;
            }
            
            .page-header {
                padding: 30px 0;
            }
            
            .page-header-content {
                padding: 0 24px;
            }
            
            .page-title {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            
            .container {
                padding: 40px 24px 60px;
            }
            
            .content {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <a href="/" class="logo">Paper Trails</a>
            <nav class="header-nav">
                <a href="/" class="nav-link">← Back to feed</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="page-header">
        <div class="page-header-content">
            <h1 class="page-title">About Paper Trails</h1>
            <p class="page-subtitle">
                Thoughtfully curating exceptional writing from leading newsletters and publications
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                In an age of information overload, quality writing can be hard to find. Paper Trails exists to surface exceptional articles from thoughtful minds across diverse fields—helping you discover insights that matter.
            </p>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p>
                    We believe that great ideas deserve great presentation. Every article in our collection has been chosen for its depth, clarity, and unique perspective.
                </p>
            </div>

            <h2>What We Curate</h2>
            <p>Our collection spans five key areas:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Technology</strong> — Innovation, digital culture, and the future of computing</li>
                <li><strong>Politics</strong> — Governance, policy analysis, and democratic discourse</li>
                <li><strong>Economics</strong> — Markets, financial systems, and economic thinking</li>
                <li><strong>Science</strong> — Research breakthroughs and scientific understanding</li>
                <li><strong>Philosophy</strong> — Big ideas, ethics, and human nature</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Our Process</h2>
            <p>
                Each article is carefully selected from leading newsletters, independent publications, and thought leaders. We prioritize:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Original insights and fresh perspectives</li>
                <li>Clear, accessible writing that respects your time</li>
                <li>Diverse viewpoints and rigorous thinking</li>
                <li>Content that sparks meaningful reflection</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Why Paper Trails?</h2>
            <p>
                Rather than algorithmic feeds optimized for engagement, we offer human-curated selections optimized for understanding. Every article represents a deliberate choice—a signal worth your attention in a noisy world.
            </p>

            <p>
                <a href="/">Start exploring</a> our curated collection, or browse by category to find topics that resonate with your interests.
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>